-Yes.
-Do it with us.

142
00:08:22,668 --> 00:08:24,637
-Okay.
-If we're here, you'll get it.

143
00:08:25,404 --> 00:08:27,840
<i>The others came back right away.</i>

144
00:08:30,209 --> 00:08:32,945
<i>He was concerned about this sequence.</i>

145
00:08:34,113 --> 00:08:34,947
