Hear the sound and then do it.

155
00:09:10,449 --> 00:09:11,284
...Like that?

156
00:09:11,350 --> 00:09:14,253
Not quite. It's not that kind of song.

157
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,755
Yeah, but that's it.

158
00:09:15,821 --> 00:09:16,789
I can't.

159
00:09:16,856 --> 00:09:18,591
-You can.
-I'm nervous.

160
00:09:21,494 --> 00:09:23,195
<i>Before the performance.</i>

161
00:09:24,330 --> 00:09:26,532
We're going to give this to Sakurai.

162
00:09:28,167 --> 00:09:30,069
<i>In fact, the day before...</i>

163
00:09:30,636 --> 00:09:33,906
Welcome to <i>Sekai Kindan no Hakobiya</i>.

164
00:09:33,973 --> 00:09:37,143
<i>Kikuchi finished his first
prime-time show as host.</i>

165
00:09:37,209 --> 00:09:41,013
<i>Afterward, he spoke about
his senior, Sakurai.</i>

166
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:44,584
Tomorrow, we're on <i>The Music Day</i>.

167
00:09:44,650 --> 00:09:46,118
We'll be, you know...

168
00:09:46,185 --> 00:09:51,090
We'll have the honor
of recording a segment.

169
00:09:51,157 --> 00:09:56,896
Sho Sakurai is the MC

170
00:09:57,830 --> 00:09:59,632
and he said that tomorrow...

171
00:10:00,633 --> 00:10:02,268
