172
00:10:02,335 --> 00:10:06,205
He told me that himself.

173
00:10:06,272 --> 00:10:08,841
{\an8}Originally, it was just the five of us

174
00:10:08,908 --> 00:10:11,110
{\an8}going there to record it alone.

175
00:10:11,711 --> 00:10:15,848
{\an8}And then that would be used
during the live broadcast.

176
00:10:17,917 --> 00:10:20,686
But he said, "Since it's all five of you,

177
00:10:22,488 --> 00:10:26,225
it's important for me to be there."

178
00:10:28,027 --> 00:10:29,261
It was...

179
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:33,099
It was really moving.

180
00:10:38,938 --> 00:10:40,539
-Hi.
-Good to see you.

181
00:10:40,606 --> 00:10:41,974
Thank you for today.

182
00:10:42,642 --> 00:10:43,809
Thank you for coming.

183
