191
00:11:05,564 --> 00:11:07,233
Thank you very much.

192
00:11:07,299 --> 00:11:08,501
I can't wait.

193
00:11:08,567 --> 00:11:09,902
Thank you very much.

194
00:11:09,969 --> 00:11:11,737
