Don't lie.

199
00:11:17,777 --> 00:11:19,645
Thank you. Goodbye.

200
00:11:19,712 --> 00:11:20,713
Sexy thank you!

201
00:11:20,780 --> 00:11:21,647
Thank you sexy too!

202
00:11:24,517 --> 00:11:26,118
{\an8}<i>Then, the shoot.</i>

203
00:11:26,185 --> 00:11:27,586
{\an8}-Hey, So.
-Yes!

204
00:11:27,653 --> 00:11:28,487
{\an8}Welcome back.

205
00:11:28,554 --> 00:11:30,156
{\an8}Thanks! Sorry for the wait.

206
00:11:30,222 --> 00:11:31,891
How are you feeling?

207
00:11:31,957 --> 00:11:35,761
I'm very happy to be
able to perform as five.

208
00:11:35,828 --> 00:11:39,598
And these four gave me
such a warm welcome. I'm really happy.

209
00:11:39,665 --> 00:11:43,202
Seeing the five of you together
makes me happy too.

210
00:11:43,269 --> 00:11:45,037
Everyone, places please.

211
00:11:45,104 --> 00:11:47,039
Thank you!

212
00:12:06,358 --> 00:12:09,328
<i>Here's that part of the performance.</i>

213
00:12:21,574 --> 00:12:23,476
<i>This is how Sexy Zone</i>

214
00:12:23,542 --> 00:12:26,946
<i>launched their new beginning
in the best possible way.</i>

215
00:12:30,249 --> 00:12:32,518
Thank you very much!

216
00:12:32,585 --> 00:12:33,753
That was great.

217
00:12:36,288 --> 00:12:38,924
Wow, I was so nervous.

218
00:12:39,492 --> 00:12:44,430
Performing with all five of us,
I feel, is really great.

219
00:12:45,164 --> 00:12:47,700
With So there,

220
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:52,238
the atmosphere is warmer,
our laughs are friendlier.

221
00:12:52,905 --> 00:12:57,576
He's like the connector between bandmates.

222
00:12:57,643 --> 00:13:01,080
It's part of So's character.

223
00:13:01,981 --> 00:13:04,383
That's how he does it.

224
00:13:05,084 --> 00:13:08,254
Appearing as a five-man group

225
00:13:09,288 --> 00:13:12,858
makes a difference
when he's with us. We're stronger.

226
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:14,493
{\an8}5 MEMBERS

227
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:17,897
{\an8}<i>The insistence on having five members.</i>

228
00:13:18,597 --> 00:13:22,501
{\an8}<i>This is a part of Sexy Zone's history.</i>

229
00:13:24,170 --> 00:13:29,642
There was a time when
there were just three of us.

230
00:13:29,708 --> 00:13:31,777
We've been through a lot.

231
00:13:32,978 --> 00:13:35,381
But the fact that we are five,

232
00:13:36,248 --> 00:13:40,186
that was one core element for me.

233
00:13:42,688 --> 00:13:46,225
{\an8}<i>From 2014, Sexy Zone did in fact</i>

234
00:13:46,792 --> 00:13:51,363
{\an8}<i>operate as a three-man group
with Sato, Nakajima, and Kikuchi.</i>

235
00:13:52,198 --> 00:13:54,200
{\an8}<i>Marius and Matsushima</i>

236
00:13:54,266 --> 00:13:57,436
{\an8}<i>each had formed their own subunits.</i>

237
00:13:57,503 --> 00:13:58,404
{\an8}MARIUS YO
SEXY BOYZ

238
00:13:58,470 --> 00:13:59,371
{\an8}SO MATSUSHIMA
SEXY SHO

239
00:13:59,438 --> 00:14:01,907
The fans really got the wrong impression.

240
00:14:01,974 --> 00:14:08,781
They kept saying, "Marius and So
were kicked out of Sexy Zone."

241
00:14:08,848 --> 00:14:13,953
It's true that it looked that way,

242
00:14:14,019 --> 00:14:15,888
but I thought of it positively.

243
00:14:15,955 --> 00:14:19,792
"Now's my chance to improve myself."

244
00:14:19,859 --> 00:14:21,493
That's how I felt.

245
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:24,964
I am glad we went back to
five members now though.

246
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:29,034
Back then, it was simply a matter of age.

247
00:14:29,101 --> 00:14:32,605
I didn't understand how anything worked.

248
00:14:32,671 --> 00:14:36,609
"Why am I working apart from those three?"

249
00:14:36,675 --> 00:14:39,178
